# Assets Term Loans Amount

## identifier
de7480

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of term loans receivable by the reporting party as at the relevant date. This item is to be determined in accordance with accounting standards.

Term loans are non securitised debt financing with a specified maturity date by which the loan must be repaid.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.TermLoans.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
